Join Rapunzel Ear Surgery game and get ready to play the role of her family doctor who is sufficient enough to take care of any problem related to ear! Zoom out with a machine to clean all the debris and get her back to the normal life! Play more html5 doctor mobile games on atmegame.com without download!
